BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Triangle Board Games & Bars
UID:event_313639816@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260322T025515Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260326T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260326T230000
SUMMARY:Play Board Games at the Geekery
DESCRIPTION:Triangle Board Games and Bars\nCome play games at Gamers Geeke
 ry and Tavern every thursday night!\n\nStarting time is 6:30\, but feel fr
 ee to come in anytime and just hang out for the night. Group is very casua
 l and friendly.\n\nHow it works:\nCome on in\, grab a name tag and pay the
  $2.50 meetup participant fee at the bar area\, find the tables that are r
 eserved for the Meetup group\, play games with others who show up. Food an
 d drinks are available at the bar.\n\nPlease RSVP by noon day of. If less 
 than four people are able to attend a given Wednesday the event will be ca
 nceled.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/triangle-board-games-and-bars/events/
 313639816/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260304T225901Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T225901Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Triangle Board Games & Bars
UID:event_dpfkwtyjcfblc@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260322T025515Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T150000
SUMMARY:Euchre or cards
DESCRIPTION:Triangle Board Games and Bars\nThis is a regular Euchre and ca
 rd meetup the 2nd and 4 Saturday afternoons.\nThe location is Geekery and 
 Tavern in McGregor in Village. There is a bar with drinks and food\, we as
 k that you support them and there is a $10 table fee but we can stay and p
 lay all day. We will split the fee by 4 so $2.50 a person. The $2.50 fee c
 an be paid to the venue by talking to any of the bartenders.\nBeginners ar
 e always welcome. We can't grow if we don't teach new players! Let me know
  if you want to help organize when I am out.\nBefore we get even 4s\, we w
 ill play other card games like The Crew or Seers Catalog. Also might play 
 Tichu if there is enough interest.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/triangle-board-games-and-bars/events/
 dpfkwtyjcfblc/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260308T213909Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260308T213909Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
